1
00:00:00,760 --> 00:00:03,560
♪Shrugging off past burdens♪

2
00:00:03,560 --> 00:00:06,150
♪Beneath the mask, who am I?♪

3
00:00:06,820 --> 00:00:10,220
♪Release and find wider shores♪

4
00:00:11,920 --> 00:00:14,930
♪Love's a riddle, and rain pours heavy♪

5
00:00:15,300 --> 00:00:17,830
♪Crossed paths, now downward fall♪

6
00:00:18,170 --> 00:00:21,610
♪From dust arises starlight's spark♪

7
00:00:23,360 --> 00:00:28,580
♪Tearing through
the night's dense blockade♪

8
00:00:29,260 --> 00:00:34,340
♪Heart's flame illuminates all solitude♪

9
00:00:35,140 --> 00:00:37,630
♪Let time's sails drift endlessly♪

10
00:00:37,630 --> 00:00:40,240
♪Through wandering exile♪

11
00:00:40,760 --> 00:00:48,020
♪Breaking free from the cocoon,
I start anew♪

12
00:00:48,990 --> 00:00:51,750
♪Moon as song, life as flame♪

13
00:00:51,810 --> 00:00:54,650
♪Nameless heart clings fiercely♪

14
00:00:54,940 --> 00:00:55,970
♪Let me♪

15
00:00:56,160 --> 00:01:00,240
♪Charge toward the next raging river♪

16
00:01:00,690 --> 00:01:03,370
♪Moon darts, snow falls♪

17
00:01:03,660 --> 00:01:06,360
♪We tread rugged paths to reunite♪

18
00:01:06,530 --> 00:01:08,000
♪Hands held tight♪

19
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:12,170
♪We forever live for love's sake♪

20
00:01:12,530 --> 00:01:22,780
♪Shadow's spear burns fiercely♪

21
00:01:24,210 --> 00:01:29,760
=Legend of The Female General=

22
00:01:30,300 --> 00:01:30,940
That's all

23
00:01:31,300 --> 00:01:32,580
for today.

24
00:01:33,060 --> 00:01:34,100
Remember

25
00:01:34,660 --> 00:01:36,340
to review what you've learned.

26
00:01:37,140 --> 00:01:37,820
Tomorrow,

27
00:01:38,060 --> 00:01:40,380
I will personally test you.

28
00:01:43,580 --> 00:01:44,220
Understood.

29
00:01:48,660 --> 00:01:50,420
He always wears a mask.

30
00:01:51,020 --> 00:01:52,220
What's wrong with him?

31
00:01:54,140 --> 00:01:54,700
You'll know.

32
00:01:57,370 --> 00:01:58,020
(Huainanzi)

33
00:01:58,979 --> 00:01:59,740
Give it back!

34
00:01:59,860 --> 00:02:00,740
Come take it back.

35
00:02:01,420 --> 00:02:02,100
Come on!

36
00:02:02,860 --> 00:02:03,540
Come get it.

37
00:02:03,980 --> 00:02:04,500
Come on.

38
00:02:04,780 --> 00:02:05,320
Come on.

39
00:02:05,500 --> 00:02:06,500
You can't get it.

40
00:02:09,419 --> 00:02:10,419
You can't get it.

41
00:02:12,260 --> 00:02:12,900
Give it back!

42
00:02:14,740 --> 00:02:15,340
Give it back!

43
00:02:21,940 --> 00:02:22,470
Let's go.

44
00:02:25,740 --> 00:02:26,260
Thanks.

45
00:02:26,740 --> 00:02:27,500
Short and dumb.

46
00:02:28,140 --> 00:02:28,660
I wonder

47
00:02:28,660 --> 00:02:29,780
how you got in.

48
00:02:30,620 --> 00:02:31,740
You eat more at night.

49
00:02:35,780 --> 00:02:36,660
Xianchang Academy

50
00:02:36,660 --> 00:02:37,780
doesn't select me by height.

51
00:02:38,660 --> 00:02:39,220
Besides,

52
00:02:39,780 --> 00:02:40,420
I'm not dumb.

53
00:02:50,490 --> 00:02:53,480
=Episode 3=

54
00:04:09,740 --> 00:04:10,860
Bye, Commander Xiao.

55
00:04:12,020 --> 00:04:12,700
It's you again.

56
00:04:13,830 --> 00:04:15,730
(Xiao)

57
00:04:56,140 --> 00:04:57,100
He's doing great today.

58
00:04:57,460 --> 00:04:58,380
He doesn't lag behind.

59
00:04:59,340 --> 00:05:00,700
When fighting me yesterday,

60
00:05:01,340 --> 00:05:02,860
he wasn't weak at all.

61
00:05:03,700 --> 00:05:04,940
So, he's been pretending.

62
00:05:05,740 --> 00:05:07,260
Seems we need a more enticing bait.

63
00:05:07,860 --> 00:05:08,940
Let's see

64
00:05:08,940 --> 00:05:10,460
when his true colors emerge.

65
00:05:11,300 --> 00:05:12,340
Since you've doubted

66
00:05:12,340 --> 00:05:13,500
He Yan's identity,

67
00:05:13,900 --> 00:05:15,020
why stay quiet?

68
00:05:15,860 --> 00:05:17,180
When fighting him,

69
00:05:17,820 --> 00:05:19,780
I sensed his physical weakness,

70
00:05:20,220 --> 00:05:22,060
yet his moves flowed effortlessly.

71
00:05:22,700 --> 00:05:24,180
Clearly, he's not an amateur.

72
00:05:25,100 --> 00:05:26,380
He's slippery.

73
00:05:27,220 --> 00:05:28,260
Without solid evidence,

74
00:05:28,260 --> 00:05:29,300
he won't confess.

75
00:05:30,300 --> 00:05:31,220
Our task

76
00:05:31,940 --> 00:05:33,940
is to expose his flaws openly.

77
00:05:39,220 --> 00:05:39,780
Shen Han.

78
00:05:41,460 --> 00:05:42,580
Do something for me.

79
00:05:44,700 --> 00:05:45,290
Yes.

80
00:05:48,340 --> 00:05:49,380
- Let me help you.
- Move.

81
00:05:49,380 --> 00:05:50,060
Come on!

82
00:06:12,220 --> 00:06:13,320
(Jiuqi Camp)

83
00:06:37,380 --> 00:06:38,300
So impressive!

84
00:06:47,940 --> 00:06:48,740
If I could

85
00:06:49,020 --> 00:06:49,860
be as brave as them,

86
00:06:49,860 --> 00:06:50,570
that'd be great.

87
00:06:50,780 --> 00:06:51,900
Who are they?

88
00:06:52,100 --> 00:06:53,020
Why so valiant?

89
00:06:53,420 --> 00:06:54,140
Jiuqi Camp.

90
00:06:54,740 --> 00:06:55,780
Jiuqi Camp?

91
00:06:56,380 --> 00:06:57,540
What's that?

92
00:06:57,780 --> 00:06:58,700
You don't know?

93
00:06:58,900 --> 00:07:00,180
It was founded by Marshal Xiao.

94
00:07:00,860 --> 00:07:02,100
It accepts elite warriors only.

95
00:07:02,540 --> 00:07:03,580
All in black armor.

96
00:07:04,100 --> 00:07:05,380
They're invincible,

97
00:07:05,700 --> 00:07:06,900
the core force of Xiao Army.

98
00:07:07,180 --> 00:07:08,140
All enemies fear them.

99
00:07:08,540 --> 00:07:09,300
Why's everyone

100
00:07:09,740 --> 00:07:10,980
suddenly talking about them?

101
00:07:11,340 --> 00:07:12,060
Someone

102
00:07:12,060 --> 00:07:13,020
started it.

103
00:07:13,540 --> 00:07:14,220
But no one

104
00:07:14,220 --> 00:07:15,340
would refuse joining, right?

105
00:07:19,540 --> 00:07:21,020
(They're talking about Jiuqi Camp.)

106
00:07:21,980 --> 00:07:23,740
(Could it be planned?)

107
00:07:25,740 --> 00:07:27,340
(Xiao Jue noticed something)

108
00:07:27,820 --> 00:07:29,260
(during last night's fight.)

109
00:07:29,980 --> 00:07:31,300
(He set a bait)

110
00:07:31,540 --> 00:07:32,659
(to hook me.)

111
00:07:34,460 --> 00:07:35,140
(Baiting me?)

112
00:07:35,700 --> 00:07:36,860
(I'll play along)

113
00:07:37,060 --> 00:07:37,860
(and join the camp.)

114
00:07:38,580 --> 00:07:40,060
(I will do it honorably,)

115
00:07:40,220 --> 00:07:40,940
(flawlessly.)

116
00:07:41,780 --> 00:07:43,220
(Who's bait? Who's prey?)

117
00:07:43,460 --> 00:07:44,420
(Game's still on.)

118
00:07:45,180 --> 00:07:45,770
Mr. Shen.

119
00:07:46,420 --> 00:07:47,020
Mr. Shen.

120
00:07:48,060 --> 00:07:48,580
Zoning out?

121
00:07:50,500 --> 00:07:51,020
Mr. Shen.

122
00:07:53,420 --> 00:07:54,150
Work harder,

123
00:07:54,540 --> 00:07:55,740
and you can join them too.

124
00:07:56,180 --> 00:07:57,060
They're so formidable.

125
00:07:57,260 --> 00:07:58,060
I'm joining them.

126
00:08:03,340 --> 00:08:04,620
Don't rush to join them

127
00:08:04,620 --> 00:08:05,460
just because of that.

128
00:08:05,700 --> 00:08:07,260
They often spearhead the frontlines,

129
00:08:07,420 --> 00:08:08,140
where casualties

130
00:08:08,140 --> 00:08:09,100
remain alarmingly high.

131
00:08:09,620 --> 00:08:10,460
That's perfect then.

132
00:08:11,020 --> 00:08:12,100
They need fresh recruits.

133
00:08:12,300 --> 00:08:13,300
I need military merits.

134
00:08:13,740 --> 00:08:14,860
If I join the Jiuqi Camp,

135
00:08:15,140 --> 00:08:16,100
it's win-win.

136
00:08:18,300 --> 00:08:19,020
We do

137
00:08:19,020 --> 00:08:20,540
select one recruit annually.

138
00:08:20,900 --> 00:08:21,510
However,

139
00:08:21,820 --> 00:08:23,620
it must be
the most outstanding candidate.

140
00:08:24,340 --> 00:08:24,900
This year,

141
00:08:25,540 --> 00:08:26,740
save yourselves the trouble.

142
00:08:27,380 --> 00:08:28,460
The best candidate is

143
00:08:29,140 --> 00:08:29,940
right before you.

144
00:08:31,980 --> 00:08:32,580
Good.

145
00:08:32,900 --> 00:08:34,299
I'll be watching your performance.

146
00:08:41,700 --> 00:08:42,460
He.

147
00:08:42,460 --> 00:08:43,020
Come quick!

148
00:08:43,220 --> 00:08:44,100
Look, meat flatbreads.

149
00:08:52,940 --> 00:08:53,660
That flatbread

150
00:08:54,180 --> 00:08:54,820
is mine.

151
00:08:55,420 --> 00:08:56,220
Yours?

152
00:08:57,180 --> 00:08:57,940
Call its name

153
00:08:58,500 --> 00:08:59,620
and see if it answers you.

154
00:09:00,380 --> 00:09:01,860
Who can prove this is yours?

155
00:09:02,700 --> 00:09:03,500
I'm eating it.

156
00:09:03,780 --> 00:09:04,660
What can you do?

157
00:09:05,780 --> 00:09:06,940
What can I do about it?

158
00:09:11,820 --> 00:09:12,420
You...

159
00:09:12,500 --> 00:09:13,220
You...

160
00:09:14,060 --> 00:09:14,630
Yes.

161
00:09:15,180 --> 00:09:15,820
I did it.

162
00:09:16,180 --> 00:09:16,980
Who can verify that?

163
00:09:17,780 --> 00:09:18,940
What can you do about it?

164
00:09:20,060 --> 00:09:20,580
You...

165
00:09:21,540 --> 00:09:22,060
Want a fight?

166
00:09:24,900 --> 00:09:25,510
Fine.

167
00:09:25,980 --> 00:09:27,180
Wait for me after training.

168
00:09:27,180 --> 00:09:28,100
I'll make you pay.

169
00:09:29,060 --> 00:09:30,020
Enough, He.

170
00:09:30,300 --> 00:09:31,500
Don't stoop to his level.

171
00:09:32,140 --> 00:09:33,260
Since he took my food once,

172
00:09:33,900 --> 00:09:34,780
he might do it again.

173
00:09:35,700 --> 00:09:36,740
If he takes my food daily,

174
00:09:37,460 --> 00:09:38,300
should I starve

175
00:09:38,300 --> 00:09:39,060
every single day?

176
00:09:39,700 --> 00:09:40,220
That is

177
00:09:40,860 --> 00:09:42,220
so not fair.

178
00:09:42,460 --> 00:09:43,860
Are you talking with me

179
00:09:43,860 --> 00:09:45,100
about fairness?

180
00:09:46,220 --> 00:09:47,220
With your weakness,

181
00:09:47,420 --> 00:09:48,140
you won't

182
00:09:48,420 --> 00:09:49,700
survive a month here.

183
00:09:50,020 --> 00:09:50,740
Not even a month.

184
00:09:51,220 --> 00:09:52,060
No need to wait.

185
00:09:52,900 --> 00:09:53,620
In ten days,

186
00:09:54,060 --> 00:09:54,820
at training field,

187
00:09:55,660 --> 00:09:57,180
I'll defeat you in archery,

188
00:09:58,020 --> 00:09:59,340
your best skill.

189
00:10:03,940 --> 00:10:05,820
Are you crazy?

190
00:10:06,220 --> 00:10:08,420
You understand your own words?

191
00:10:08,780 --> 00:10:09,500
Which part

192
00:10:09,500 --> 00:10:10,540
did you not hear?

193
00:10:11,460 --> 00:10:12,660
Let me repeat myself.

194
00:10:13,540 --> 00:10:14,340
In ten days,

195
00:10:15,060 --> 00:10:16,460
I will defeat you.

196
00:10:17,580 --> 00:10:18,380
Pretty boy,

197
00:10:18,980 --> 00:10:20,100
you're very bold.

198
00:10:22,020 --> 00:10:22,540
Alright.

199
00:10:22,860 --> 00:10:24,100
That's a bold wager.

200
00:10:24,100 --> 00:10:25,300
- Yes.
- Good.

201
00:10:25,620 --> 00:10:26,780
If you lose,

202
00:10:27,620 --> 00:10:29,380
you'll become an army cook.

203
00:10:30,180 --> 00:10:30,790
Deal.

204
00:10:31,300 --> 00:10:32,500
But if you lose,

205
00:10:33,180 --> 00:10:34,060
you'll call me boss.

206
00:10:38,860 --> 00:10:39,900
Don't humiliate yourself.

207
00:10:40,740 --> 00:10:41,780
In ten days,

208
00:10:42,500 --> 00:10:44,060
I'll challenge you to a spear duel.

209
00:10:44,500 --> 00:10:45,500
Do you dare to accept it?

210
00:10:46,820 --> 00:10:48,420
Since you're so reckless,

211
00:10:48,940 --> 00:10:49,860
I'll play along.

212
00:10:51,900 --> 00:10:52,490
Good.

213
00:10:53,180 --> 00:10:54,300
In ten days,

214
00:10:55,020 --> 00:10:56,380
we'll compete.

215
00:10:56,900 --> 00:10:57,420
How dare you!

216
00:10:58,340 --> 00:10:59,700
- Commander.
- Commander.

217
00:10:59,900 --> 00:11:01,740
Brawling right after joining the army?

218
00:11:02,060 --> 00:11:03,660
Have you no respect for discipline?

219
00:11:04,500 --> 00:11:05,100
It's okay.

220
00:11:06,860 --> 00:11:08,420
He wants to join the Jiuqi Camp.

221
00:11:09,340 --> 00:11:10,260
I'll see

222
00:11:11,020 --> 00:11:12,420
if he's qualified.

223
00:11:42,930 --> 00:11:44,370
♪I've seen the mountains♪

224
00:11:44,560 --> 00:11:45,920
♪And trodden through ice♪

225
00:11:46,070 --> 00:11:48,600
♪Day after day, I venture alone♪

226
00:11:48,900 --> 00:11:50,610
♪Destiny is my creed♪

227
00:11:50,760 --> 00:11:52,160
♪Ideals surge beneath the surface♪

228
00:11:52,310 --> 00:11:54,110
♪Igniting the flame against the winds♪

229
00:11:55,310 --> 00:11:56,780
♪A restless yearning in my soul♪

230
00:11:56,950 --> 00:11:58,230
♪Gazing through the mire♪

231
00:11:58,410 --> 00:12:00,800
♪Who cares about this boundless void♪

232
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:03,050
♪Charge ahead with blazing fervor♪

233
00:12:04,190 --> 00:12:06,020
♪Stubbornly fighting with my life♪

234
00:12:07,980 --> 00:12:10,900
♪Soaring across the world's expanse♪

235
00:12:10,980 --> 00:12:13,650
♪There must always be a longing♪

236
00:12:14,100 --> 00:12:19,160
♪Disregard the wounds to seek the light♪

237
00:12:19,500 --> 00:12:21,510
♪Light shines upon my heart♪

238
00:12:21,820 --> 00:12:25,470
♪Unveiling scars,
I choose to swim upstream♪

239
00:12:25,700 --> 00:12:27,590
♪The resonance of courage
rings loud and clear♪

240
00:12:27,620 --> 00:12:31,470
♪It's the boldness
that defines existence♪

241
00:12:31,820 --> 00:12:33,760
♪Chasing the light within my heart♪

242
00:12:33,950 --> 00:12:37,770
♪Burying frailty,
embracing life through death♪

243
00:12:38,030 --> 00:12:43,780
♪You'll meet gazes where storms brew♪

244
00:12:44,670 --> 00:12:50,130
♪With our unwavering true love,
brave the world with me♪

245
00:12:57,540 --> 00:12:58,420
You work so hard,

246
00:12:59,140 --> 00:13:00,460
yet you're still weak.

247
00:13:08,260 --> 00:13:10,060
The sneaky person at the bathing pool

248
00:13:11,740 --> 00:13:12,540
was you, right?

249
00:13:16,260 --> 00:13:17,060
A while ago,

250
00:13:17,220 --> 00:13:18,860
I was exhausted from training.

251
00:13:19,180 --> 00:13:20,540
So, I went to bathe to relax.

252
00:13:22,340 --> 00:13:24,020
The person who was bathing that night

253
00:13:24,500 --> 00:13:25,660
was actually you.

254
00:13:26,500 --> 00:13:27,380
However,

255
00:13:27,620 --> 00:13:29,020
I panicked and fled recklessly

256
00:13:29,300 --> 00:13:30,060
that night.

257
00:13:30,460 --> 00:13:31,820
I hope you won't blame me.

258
00:13:33,060 --> 00:13:34,220
You panicked?

259
00:13:34,660 --> 00:13:36,220
Sure, I did.

260
00:13:39,820 --> 00:13:40,860
You're suspicious

261
00:13:41,420 --> 00:13:42,380
and a liar.

262
00:13:42,940 --> 00:13:44,460
What's your real intention?

263
00:13:46,500 --> 00:13:47,720
I want a trainer.

264
00:13:48,580 --> 00:13:49,220
What?

265
00:13:52,380 --> 00:13:53,060
No offense,

266
00:13:53,540 --> 00:13:55,100
but please train me, Commander.

267
00:14:00,860 --> 00:14:01,780
What makes you think

268
00:14:02,380 --> 00:14:03,020
I'll train you?

269
00:14:05,420 --> 00:14:06,460
Otherwise, did you

270
00:14:06,940 --> 00:14:08,380
come out so late at night

271
00:14:08,660 --> 00:14:09,860
to ambush a recruit for fun?

272
00:14:11,020 --> 00:14:11,620
I know

273
00:14:12,180 --> 00:14:13,420
you're concerned about me.

274
00:14:14,020 --> 00:14:14,620
You think

275
00:14:14,620 --> 00:14:15,820
I have potential.

276
00:14:16,420 --> 00:14:17,500
Practice needs a partner.

277
00:14:17,740 --> 00:14:18,820
Practicing alone

278
00:14:19,140 --> 00:14:19,980
won't work out.

279
00:14:20,740 --> 00:14:22,660
If you train me,

280
00:14:23,020 --> 00:14:25,220
I'm certain I'll make great progress.

281
00:14:25,860 --> 00:14:27,140
Quite cheeky.

282
00:14:34,420 --> 00:14:35,580
If you can resist ten strikes

283
00:14:35,580 --> 00:14:36,380
in a circle,

284
00:14:37,420 --> 00:14:38,380
I'll train you.

285
00:14:41,060 --> 00:14:41,660
Deal.

286
00:15:43,540 --> 00:15:44,420
Can't even hold it.

287
00:15:44,860 --> 00:15:45,900
Why should I train you?

288
00:15:46,100 --> 00:15:46,660
I...

289
00:16:27,180 --> 00:16:27,820
Commander.

290
00:16:28,700 --> 00:16:29,660
Ten strikes done.

291
00:16:31,340 --> 00:16:32,020
I'm still in.

292
00:16:41,180 --> 00:16:42,020
My fault.

293
00:16:42,580 --> 00:16:43,140
Accidentally,

294
00:16:44,420 --> 00:16:45,580
I offended you.

295
00:16:50,260 --> 00:16:50,820
Commander.

296
00:16:51,380 --> 00:16:52,100
A promise

297
